snippet.title: Ion Fury Aftershock - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Finally after a delay fit for a king, Ion Fury: Aftershock can be yours! On October 2nd--the Monday following Realms Deep--you can pick up Ion Fury: Aftershock. 

- Buy Ion Fury Aftershock here: https://3drealms.live/IonFuryAftershock
